    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "AI LA PAZ (BOLIVIA),from left to\nright,\nManager of Grace y Cia. (Bolivia);Mr. Gerhard Gessell;Mr. Harold .\nMr. Nevaldo Rocha,President of Lloya Aéreo Boliviano;and\nJ.A. Wilbur of Grace y",
      "RANAGRA",
      "ARRIVAL AT LA PAZ' \"EL ALTO\" AIRPORI of Mr. Harold J.Roig\nand\nMr. Gerhard Gessell on July 2,1943.",
      "Mr.\nHarold J. Roig's\npress\nconference which took place\nat his suite in the Carrera Hotel was\nattended by reporters from\nall papers and news services.\nFrom left to right: Mr.\nMario Quiros\nPanagra Chief Publicity; Mr. Roig; and Mr. Cristian\nTrampe from\nth\nAssociated Press.",
      "PANAGRA\nRAA\nDU\nARGENTINA",
      "Mr. Josh Lee, Chairman of the Civil Aeronautics Boara,\nthe press conference in the Hotel Carrera.",
      "WAKS, /\nThe American Ambassador Mr. Claude G. Bowers\nwas at\nLos Cerrillos Airport to greet Mr. Roig and Mr. Lee. From left\nto right: Mr. Roig, Mr. Bowers and Mr. Lee.",
      "ARWAKS,\nPAMAGg, PANAGe,\nALE",
      "Mr. Harold J. Roig posed for this photograph for\nRevista\nVea the day he arrived to Santiago."
